Phoenix Solar Expects 2011 Sales Unchanged or Marginally Higher

-- B y   R a j i v   S e k h r i
-- 
2011-04-18T05:39:01Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-18/phoenix-solar-expects-2011-sales-unchanged-or-marginally-higher.html
Phoenix Solar AG (PS4)  expects sales in
2011 to be unchanged or marginally higher than last year, the
company said in a statement today.  It said it saw very weak markets in the first quarter. The
company said it expects stronger growth in revenue and earnings
before interest and tax in 2012.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Rajiv Sekhri at 
 rsekhri1@bloomberg.net  